 _5"></span>吃肉跟</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y20e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">吃生命没什么差别，<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="lsf">是需要严格遮止的。<span class="_ _9"></span>与汉传佛教比起来，</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y200 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">藏传佛教以前在这方面做得不太好，<span class="_ _5"></span>但这几年来，<span class="_ _5"></span>藏传佛教</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y201 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的很多寺院和出家人，也都开始纷纷提倡素食。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y202 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">今天中午，<span class="_ _3"></span>我为了找个地方吃饭，<span class="_ _3"></span>转了好几圈，<span class="_ _3"></span>结果发</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
